1
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,350
<i>Mom?</i>

2
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,628
<i>Come on, guys, push it!</i>

3
00:03:44,022 --> 00:03:46,962
<i>Move when you got the ball!
