505
00:48:42,260 --> 00:48:45,120
<i>So was it used for
something religious?</i>

506
00:48:45,121 --> 00:48:47,650
<i>The more traditional
branches of Judaism,</i>

507
00:48:47,651 --> 00:48:50,243
<i>especially in the Hasidic sects...</i>

508
00:48:50,244 --> 00:48:55,558
<i>...believe in various spirits,
both benevolent and, um...</i>

509
00:48:57,112 --> 00:49:01,816
