00:49:48,810 --> 00:49:51,657
<i>"Do not open."</i>

522
00:49:51,658 --> 00:49:54,856
<i>So, don't open it.</i>

523
00:50:57,790 --> 00:51:00,004
<i>-What are you doing here?
