528
00:51:23,667 --> 00:51:24,512
<i>Em.</i>

529
00:51:34,499 --> 00:51:37,943
<i>"Whoever sits in the
refuge of the most high...</i>

530
00:51:37,944 --> 00:51:42,102
<i>"...he shall dwell in
