533
00:51:48,709 --> 00:51:51,978
<i>"I will trust in Him.</i>

534
00:51:51,979 --> 00:51:55,677
<i>"For He will deliver
you from the ensnaring trap...</i>

535
00:51:55,678 --> 00:51:57,920
<i>...from devastating pestilence..."</i>

536
00:52:05,912 --> 00:52:09,192
<i>"With his pinion He will cover you,</i>

537
00:52:09,193 --> 00:52:11,569
<i>and beneath His wings
you will be protected.</i>

538
00:52:11,570 --> 00:52:14,534
<i>"His truth is shield...</i>

539
00:52:17,431 --> 00:52:22,749
