<i>You shall not fear
the terror of night, nor--"</i>

541
00:52:36,649 --> 00:52:37,977
<i>Who are you?</i>

542
00:52:40,362 --> 00:52:43,600
<i>What do you want with
my little girl?</i>

543
00:52:45,240 --> 00:52:46,544
<i>You tell me!</i>

544
00:52:47,881 --> 00:52:49,456
<i>What do you want?</i>

545
00:52:50,173 --> 00:52:52,225
<i>You tell me!</i>

546
00:52:52,226 --> 00:52:54,153
<i>Clyde!</i>

547
00:52:54,154 --> 00:52:56,685
<i>What are you doing here? Get out!</i>

548
00:52:56,686 --> 00:53:00,322
<i>Get out of the house!
