549
00:53:54,340 --> 00:53:56,973
<i>Babylon your throne</i>

550
00:53:56,974 --> 00:53:59,763
<i>Down, down, down</i>

551
00:53:59,764 --> 00:54:05,139
<i>Babylon your throne down</i>

552
00:54:06,552 --> 00:54:11,613
<i>One bright morning
when my work is over</i>

553
00:54:11,613 --> 00:54:14,492
<i>I'm going to fly--</i>

