00:54:14,493 --> 00:54:15,999
<i>Excuse me.</i>

555
00:54:16,587 --> 00:54:17,487
<i>Sorry.</i>

556
00:54:17,488 --> 00:54:19,589
<i>I get kind of lost when I'm listening.</i>

557
00:54:19,590 --> 00:54:23,033
<i>My name is Clyde Brenek.
I'm looking for Tzadok Shapir.</i>

558
00:54:23,034 --> 00:54:24,530
<i>Yeah, that's me.</i>

559
00:54:25,014 --> 00:54:27,477
<i>-We talked on the phone.
