568
00:55:44,598 --> 00:55:46,902
<i>I bought it at a yard sale.</i>

569
00:55:46,903 --> 00:55:49,363
<i>Did you open it?</i>

570
00:55:51,097 --> 00:55:55,926
<i>Tell us, did you open the box?</i>

571
00:55:57,237 --> 00:55:59,133
<i>My daughter...</i>

572
00:55:59,134 --> 00:56:00,961
<i>My daughter opened it.</i>

573
00:56:07,579 --> 00:56:09,376
<i>What does this thing
want with my daughter?</i>

574
00:56:12,753 --> 00:56:16,354
<i>The debunk looks for innocence.
