575
00:56:16,355 --> 00:56:20,555
<i>It will move back
and forth from the box...</i>

576
00:56:20,556 --> 00:56:23,261
<i>...searching for a proper host.</i>

577
00:56:23,262 --> 00:56:27,572
<i>The host begins to hear voices...
experience visions.</i>

578
00:56:27,573 --> 00:56:30,667
<i>All of this is the
deception of the spirit...</i>

579
00:56:30,668 --> 00:56:34,069
<i>...to protect the host
