580
00:56:35,880 --> 00:56:38,894
<i>The final stage is when the
debunk attaches to the host....</i>

581
00:56:38,895 --> 00:56:41,327
<i>...the two becoming one.</i>

582
00:56:41,328 --> 00:56:45,849
<i>It will feed and take
