00:56:50,744 --> 00:56:52,447
<i>Leiben.</i>

585
00:56:52,448 --> 00:56:54,211
<i>Life.</i>

586
00:57:08,536 --> 00:57:10,996
<i>How do I stop it?</i>

587
00:57:12,317 --> 00:57:13,898
