594
00:57:39,293 --> 00:57:40,506
<i>No.</i>

595
00:57:42,107 --> 00:57:44,751
<i>No, wait. Wait, please.</i>

596
00:57:46,785 --> 00:57:50,028
<i>Someone here has to help me.</i>

597
00:57:51,381 --> 00:57:52,797
<i>It's not my little girl anymore.</i>

598
00:57:52,798 --> 00:57:57,508
<i>When I look at her,
